=== Noun ===
'''magician''' (''plural:'' '''[[magicians]]''')
# A person who plays with or practices [[magic]].
# A spiritualist or practicer of mystic arts (''often derogatory'').
# A performer of tricks or an escapologist.
# A talented craftsman or scientist.
# An person who is an enigma.

